Njikọ Rugby nke Nigeria bụ òtù na-achịkwa egwuregwu rugby league football na Naijiria.
Onye guzobere Njikọ Rugby nke Nigeria na 2018 bụ onye bụbu onye na-agba bọọlụ rugby league, Ade Adebisi onye bụ osote onye isi oche na onye isi oche Abiodun Olawale-Cole
E nyere Njikọ Rugby nke Nigeria ndị na-ekiri Rugby League European Federation, na-anọchi anya ndị na-achịkwa Njikọ rugby nke Nigeria.
A ga-asọ mpi oge izizi na 2019 na ọtụtụ klọb nwere mmekọrịta na klọb Super League.

Green Hawks nke Naịjirịa meriri Morocco iji merie 2019 Middle East Africa (MEA) Championship na Satọdee 5 Ọktoba na TBS Cricket Oval na Lagos.Ndị Green Hawks nwere obi ụtọ site n'aka ìgwè mmadụ na-eme mkpọtụ ma onye isi oche nke Rugby League International Federation (RLIF) Graeme Thompson na-ele ya anya, gosipụtara ike nke ukwuu maka ndị North Africa ka ha meriri 38-10 n'ihe bụ naanị egwuregwu nke abụọ ha na Rugby League nke mba ụwa
Ha meriri ndị asọmpi West Africa Ghana na mbido Rugby League ha na Wednesday iji banye na ngwụcha mgbe Atlas Lions nke Morocco meriri Morocco n'ụzọ ha na-aga na ngwụchi.
N'ọnọdụ nke atọ n'etiti Ghana na Cameroon, ọ bụ Ghana meriri Cameroon site na mmeri 10-4 n'enweghị mmeri.
